7.REGRESSION MODELLING FOR FORECASTING
Smart VendAI system’s connection between foot traffic and units sold are found using regression analysis. During a 12 month period, a dataset was gathered from vending machine sales record and publicly accessible foot traffic statistics for busy commercial locations.
In google colab, a basic linear regression model with foot traffic as the independent variable and units sold as the dependent variable was implemented using python.

