CONCLUSION
This business plan shows how modelling and planning techniques can be applied to design, evaluate and validate a technology driven business solution. Through the development of the Smart VendAI concept, the report illustrates the value of combining artificial intelligence, machine learning and internet of thing (IoT) technologies with structured analytical methods to compare it with real world operational challenges in vending industry. Traditional vending systems management, all of which reduce profitability and customer satisfaction. Smart VendAI directly responds to these limitations through automation, real time data collection and intelligent decision making. The use of conceptual modelling provides a clear understanding of how the system components interact, highlighting the flow of data, decision points and stakeholder involvement across the Smart VendAI ecosystem. This foundational model ensured that the business concept was logically structured before moving on to more planning process by clearly defining value propositions, revenue streams, key resources and cost structure which confirms the commercial feasibility and sustainability of the proposed business.
Regression modelling played a critical role in forecastting demand and supporting evidence based planning. By establishing a strong positive relationship between foot traffic and sales. This analysis strengthened the importance of strategic location selection and informed revenue and inventory planning decisions. This approach reduced uncertainty and improved confidence in forecasting future performance. Also, simulation using Insight Maker enables the testing of inventory strategies under different demand and real time scenario without financial risk. The stock and flow model showed us optimal reorder points, reduced stockout probability and balanced inventory levels, showing how system dynamics modelling supports long term operational stability.
Overall, the integration of modelling, forecasting and simulation provided a complete structure for analysing both technical and business viability of Smart VendAI. The findings confirms that Smart VendAI is a practical, scalable and data-driven solution capable of delivering improved efficiency, reduced costs and enhanced customer satisfaction.


